headline.print_headline: Florida Man Sentenced to Almost 60 Years for Killing NFL Star
headline.main: Florida Man Sentenced to Almost 60 Years for Killing NFL Star

lead_paragraph: A 23-year-old man convicted of second-degree murder in the 2007 killing of Washington Redskins football star Sean Taylor was sentenced to 57-1/2 years in prison on Thursday.
